data.description: Immerse yourself in the allure of your own private retreat, tailored for those who savor life's finer moments. This exceptional 2-bed, 2-bath residence, with an extra study/den, introduces you to an exclusive world crafted with the discerning 55+ individual in mind. Nestled at the serene end of a cul-de-sac, this Astor Model haven features seclusion without rear neighbors, offering unparalleled peace and tranquility. Step outdoors to your personal oasis, where a screened-in pool invites leisurely relaxation. A 2022-new roof ensures your peace of mind. The heart of any home, the kitchen, boasts granite countertops, crown molding, and top-tier stainless steel appliances, including a French door refrigerator/freezer, GE oven, and microwave. Culinary desires thrive in this well-appointed space. As you explore the residence, elegance unfolds with crown-molded ceilings nearly 10 feet high. Custom window dressings add sophistication, framing picturesque views of your private surroundings. Luxury meets practicality with upgrades like new tile, plush carpeting, ornate ceiling fans, and a surround sound system, immersing you in audio delights. The utility room features upgraded washer and dryer, simplifying daily chores. Yet, the true allure extends beyond your exquisite abode to the vibrant community. The Plantation at Leesburg, a gated 55+ haven, promises a life enriched with activities for kindred spirits. Enjoy the security of two manned gates for peace of mind. Golf enthusiasts will revel in access to two championship golf courses, a golfer's paradise at your doorstep. Three activity centers offer over 100 diverse activities, catering to various interests. Whether crafting, staying fit, or socializing, there's something for everyone. For the health-conscious, three pools and two fitness centers await your enjoyment. Engage in friendly competition with tennis, pickleball, shuffleboard, bocce, volleyball, and softball. Enjoy leisurely pier fishing or explore your artistic side with woodworking. The Pro-shop keeps you ready for golf, and an on-site restaurant invites you to savor delightful meals. Now is the time to embrace this exclusive lifestyle.
